title: 03/10/21 DPS Hour 1 Mike Florio
itunes:title: 03/10/21 DPS Hour 1 Mike Florio
description:
Mike Florio tells Dan which New York NFL team is in better shape. Mike says the giants have a shot because their division is so bad, but Mike says he likes what the Jets have going. Mike Tells Dan that we are just so used to the Jets being bad.
